reviews.text: Though small, all food in the menu is recommended. Prices are cheap with warm attitude in serving.

The food was very nice, staffs were friendly, and the price was very very reasonable!

One of their signature dishes - pork chop was especially popular. Its size, thickness and succulence were amazing.

Spicy pig knuckle was also recommended.

Its Chongqing wonton noodles was delicious too. The “skin” of wonton was very thin and the texture of noodles was quite authentic. 

The only problem of this place was that they didn’t have a gaudy look which would capture your attention.
Inexpensive tasty food.
Their dumplings and pan fried pork chop is good.  Reasonably priced.
Tender pork chop, good spicy noodle quick bite

reviews.text: 第一眼睇，以為係法國菜。厚切豬扒，貨真價實，厚過我手掌，五香味濃，雞翼煎得剛好漲卜卜，好食。
招牌厚切豬扒可以一試 價錢同區差不多

牛腩ok 我叫BB辣，但都唔算BB(請留意)

$48 整體ok
服務態度好👍不過太少嘢吃
厚切豬扒，口水雞中翼，西洋菜雲吞，次次去都必食
